## Touch Targets

### Minimum Sizes

| Element | Minimum Size | Minimum Spacing |
|---------|-------------|-----------------|
| Buttons | 44 x 44 px | 8px between targets |
| Links in text | 44px inline height | N/A |
| Icon buttons | 44 x 44 px (touch area) | 8px between targets |
| Form inputs | 44px height | 8px between fields |
| Checkboxes/radios | 44 x 44 px (touch area) | 8px between options |

### Implementation

```css
/* Ensure minimum touch target even for small visual elements */
.icon-button {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  min-width: 44px;
  min-height: 44px;
  padding: 8px;
}
```

