## Typography Scaling

### Fluid Typography

```css
/* Fluid type scale: 16px at 320px viewport, 20px at 1280px viewport */
:root {
  --font-size-base: clamp(1rem, 0.875rem + 0.5vw, 1.25rem);
  --font-size-lg: clamp(1.25rem, 1rem + 0.75vw, 1.5rem);
  --font-size-xl: clamp(1.5rem, 1.125rem + 1.25vw, 2rem);
  --font-size-2xl: clamp(2rem, 1.5rem + 1.5vw, 3rem);
}
```

### Line Length

- [ ] Body text maximum width: 65-75 characters (approximately 600px)
- [ ] Use `max-width: 65ch` for readable content columns
- [ ] Headings can be wider but should not span full viewport on desktop

