## Testing

### Device Testing Matrix

| Device Category | Representative Devices | Must Test |
|----------------|----------------------|-----------|
| Small phone | iPhone SE, Galaxy S21 | Yes |
| Large phone | iPhone 15 Pro Max, Pixel 8 | Yes |
| Tablet portrait | iPad, Galaxy Tab | Yes |
| Tablet landscape | iPad Pro | If applicable |
| Desktop | 1280px, 1920px | Yes |
| Ultrawide | 2560px+ | If applicable |

### Responsive Testing Checklist

- [ ] All breakpoints tested (xs, sm, md, lg, xl)
- [ ] Touch targets meet minimum 44x44px on mobile
- [ ] No horizontal scrollbar at any breakpoint
- [ ] Text is readable without zooming on mobile
- [ ] Forms are usable with on-screen keyboard visible
- [ ] Orientation changes handled (portrait <-> landscape)
